        <Parent_String>Early Cycladic [300020063], Cycladic [300020060], Aegean Bronze Age periods [300106927], Aegean periods [300106920], Aegean [300020059], Mediterranean (Early Western World) [300020058], Early Western World [300019255], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
